p: According to chemical analysis, 29 compounds were identified from the essential oil of the leaves from this species, and sesquiterpene hydrocarbons were predominant ( Table 1). Major compounds identified were bicyclogermacrene (17.50%), globulol (14.13%), viridiflorol (8.83%), γ-eudesmol (7.89%), α-eudesmol (6.88%), rosifoliol (4.54%), ( E)-caryophyllene (4.49%), cubeban-11-ol (4.40%), palustrol (3.83%) and α-pinene (3.22%).
